ActsAs80sHasBeen
================

This is the ultimate plugin for everyone who LOVESÀù one or both of the following: Rick Astley, and the element of surprise.
Simply install this plugin in vendor/plugins, and follow the example instructions.

Voila! Half of your links are now rickrolls. Amuse and delight friends and enemies alike!


Example
=======
	# application.rb
	
	class ApplicationController < ActionController::Base
		acts_as_80s_has_been
		...
	end


